---
---

<div class="text-center md:text-right md:max-w-4xl md:ml-auto">
  <span class="eyebrow">Environment</span>
  <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
    Train in a production-style workspace
  </h2>
  <p class="mt-4 text-lg copy-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto md:mx-0 md:ml-auto">
    Work in a browser-based setup that mirrors real engineering flow: terminal,
    branches, tests, pull requests, and iteration.
  </p>
  <div
    class="mt-10 mx-auto md:ml-auto max-w-3xl surface-card terminal-shell p-8 text-left font-mono text-sm copy-subtle"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
      <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/80" />
      <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/80" />
      <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/80" />
    </div>
    <div class="copy-muted">
      <span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">$</span> git checkout -b
      feature/auth-flow<br />
      <span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">$</span> npm run test<br />
      <span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">$</span> git commit -m "Add auth validation"<br />
      <span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">$</span> git push origin feature/auth-flow<br />
      <span class="copy-subtle">Open PR &rarr; request review &rarr; iterate &rarr; merge</span
      ><span class="terminal-cursor" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
